location.fullValue: Ammolite Plan, Seasons at Park West

data.description: Awesomely big 5 bedroom 3 bath home about 2500 square feet of living area located within the desired area of Victorville with very easy access to Highway 395. This home has modern upgrades and a thoughtful layout. There is no HOA to deal with here. The home is close to Victor Valley Mall shopping area. This home is perfect for a bigger family or anyone that wants a large area to live.  ****REDUCTION IN PRICE*****  ****FHA LOAN MAY BE ASSUMABLE**** $332K balance $2154/mo PITI 2.375% Fixed Rate. Buyer to come up with difference with secondary financing or cash to escrow. This is a fantastic opportunity for the buyer to have a very low interest rate and payment.   Current lender says it takes 60 - 90 days for loan assumption to be approved. Please verify all information.
